OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FHeavy and
OL,6,Fperhaps thundery showers at first with
OL,7,Fa risk of hail. These will gradually
OL,8,Fease through the evening. It will then
OL,9,Fstay dry overnight with clear spells
OL,10,Fdeveloping and becoming quite chilly
OL,11,Fagain.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FA dry and bright start but
OL,14,Fturning cloudy through the morning
OL,15,Fwith outbreaks of light rain spreading
OL,16,Fnorthwards in the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
